com.qtplaf.library.trading.data

Class IndicatorDataList

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.qtplaf.library.trading.data.DataList
      • com.qtplaf.library.trading.data.IndicatorDataList

  • public class IndicatorDataList
extends DataList
    A data list that retrieves its data from an indicator, thus calculating the data each time it is retrieved through the get method.
    Author:
    Miquel Sas
